[125.57862, "o", "Technical design created at `docs/helix/02-design/technical-designs/TD-001-temperature-conversion.md`. It covers:\r\n\r\n- **Single entry point** `bin/convert.js` parsing `process.argv` directly (zero dependencies)\r\n- **Two flags:** `--to-celsius` and `--to-fahrenheit` with the standard formulas\r\n- **Validation:** checks for exactly one valid flag and a finite numeric temperature\r\n- **Output:** `toFixed(1)` to stdout, exit 0 on success, exit 1 with stderr message on error\r\n- **Traceability** back to PRD features F1/F2 and user story US-001\r\n"]
